cRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1002379, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah send blessings on Muhammad and on his children, and respond to my prayer, give ear to my outcry, feel pity for my humility, hear and answer my call. Do not cut off my hope from You. Do not disconnect (my hope of getting) my means of living from You, and do not let me turn towards someone else other than You, to seek satisfaction of my this and other needs, and to make a request for fulfillment of my wants. Prior to my departure from this place make the difficult task easy for me, and settle well all my affairs in my favour, and send blessings on Muhammad and on his children, constant, increasing, unlimited and continuous blessings, and make these blessings support me and provide a medium for obtaining satisfaction of my wants; verily You are extensively generous. O Allay my desire is (mention it, go into sajdah and say:) Your favour has given me joy, and Your kindness has shown me the right way, so I beseech You in Your name and the name of Muhammad and his children, bless them all, and do not send me away disappointed.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": "اَسْاَلُكَ بِعِزَّةِ ذٰلِكَ الْاِسْمِ اَنْ تُصَلِّيَ عَلٰى مُحَمَّدٍ وَّآلِ مُحَمَّدٍ وَاَنْ تَصْرِفَ عَنِّيْ جَمِيْعَ الْآفَاتِ وَالْعَاهَاتِ وَالْاَعْرَاضِ وَالْاَمْرَاضِ وَالْخَطَايَا وَالذُّنُوْبِ وَالشَّكِّ وَالشِّرْكِ وَالْكُفْرِ وَالنِّفَاقِ وَالشِّقَاقِ وَالْغَضَبِ وَالْجَهْلِ وَالْمَقْتِ وَالضَّلَالَةِ وَالْعُسْرِ وَ